{"id": "1182", "post": "<div class=\"post-1182 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-2host-com tag-asheville tag-exclusive tag-xen\" id=\"post-1182\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/2host-4-04-128mb-xen-vps-with-2nd-month-free/\" rel=\"bookmark\">2Host \u2013 $4.04 128MB Xen VPS with 2nd Month Free</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/2host-com/\" rel=\"tag\">2host.com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/asheville/\" rel=\"tag\">asheville</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/exclusive/\" rel=\"tag\">exclusive</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> August 11, 2010 @ 1:06 am, by LowEndAdmin</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://2host.com/\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/images/2host2.jpg\" data-src=\"/media/images/2host2.jpg\" alt=\"2Host\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a> Tom from <a href=\"http://2host.com/\"><b>2Host</b></a> emailed me to about their <a href=\"http://www.webhostingtalk.com/showthread.php?t=971492\">current special promo on WHT</a>, as well as <a href=\"/blog/2host-4-04-128mb-xen-vps-with-10tb/\">their previous exclusive offer</a> for LowEndBox readers. Same deal \u2014 use promo code <b>LEB10TB</b> to get 10% off recurring discount on their Xen SATA VPS. You can get their <a href=\"https://www.2host.com/support/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=48\">A-Class</a> (ordering link) for <b>$4.04/month</b> after the discount, and you get</p><ul><li>128MB memory/256MB swap</li><li>5GB storage</li><li>10TB/month data transfer on Gbit</li><li>Xen/SolusVM</li></ul><p>Asheville NC servers as usual. And read our previous post for discussions on what you can do with this stupid large amount of data transfer quota. Moreover, Tom is willing to offer LowEndBox readers <b>2nd month free</b> \u2014 just contact them via support ticket, and mention their promotion here.</p><p>My Xen VPS with 2Host from their old offer must have been the low end box that I have kept for the longest time (since May 2009), and currently generating all the screenshots you see here (via a modified version of <a href=\"http://github.com/coderholic/PyWebShot\">PyWebShot</a>) and a few other things. Uptime 115 days. Maybe I am just lucky :)</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2F2host-4-04-128mb-xen-vps-with-2nd-month-free%2F&amp;t=2Host%20-%20%244.04%20128MB%20Xen%20VPS%20with%202nd%20Month%20Free\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=2Host%20-%20%244.04%20128MB%20Xen%20VPS%20with%202nd%20Month%20Free&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2F2host-4-04-128mb-xen-vps-with-2nd-month-free%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-la